    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Paws and Leaves?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Paws and Leaves, you play as Me, a young fox bitten by a snake and now... dying. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's like life flashing before your eyes, when you die. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll follow Me on his final journey to rediscover his memories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By his side is a charming butterfly named Ani, who will help you, sometimes more, sometimes less. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Me relies on his senses, like smelling, to locate his memories in the realm between life and death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, you'll encounter various characters, uncover their stories, and retrieve memories and keepsakes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Keepsakes aren't Me's memories; they're yours, the player's.</strong> They're scattered throughout the world and can be anything - a personal message, an image, or even a short video clip that you want to endure in our world.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through our <strong>Kickstarter</strong>, you'll have the opportunity to include one of your memories as an exclusive keepsake in the game. These submissions will become permanent collectibles, cherished and valued. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful, colorful seasons create a cute and cozy backdrop, while the poignant story and subtle &quot;jumpscares&quot; serve as a reminder: </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Me is fading. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Paws and Leaves guides you through its narrative, yet allows you to explore the breathtaking world in-between. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small &quot;open world&quot; zones invite you to discover more keepsakes, unravel their secrets, and unveil new tales. You can even fish for mementos on an old, wise turtle. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This demo is our prototype demo and limited to ~25 minutes of gameplay. The story is quiet shorter than the exploration part.</h2>",
